WEBVTT

00:11.010 --> 00:13.350
I wish the mailpony
would just come already!

00:13.500 --> 00:17.250
I can't wait another minute to find out
if Rainbow Dash got in or not!

00:17.400 --> 00:20.650
Pinkie Pie, you're more nervous
than Rainbow Dash!

00:20.800 --> 00:22.600
I'm not nervous at all!

00:22.750 --> 00:24.650
When I get into
the Wonderbolt Academy--

00:24.800 --> 00:27.050
If you get in!
If you get in!

00:27.200 --> 00:28.300
Don't jinx it!

00:28.450 --> 00:30.660
I'm telling you,
it's in the bag!

00:30.810 --> 00:31.530
Don't jinx it!

00:31.680 --> 00:33.870
She is the best flyer in Ponyville.

00:34.020 --> 00:35.500
In Ponyville?

00:37.300 --> 00:40.410
I'm probably the best flyer
in all of Equestria.

00:40.560 --> 00:41.439
I wouldn't be surprised

00:41.590 --> 00:43.340
if they just went ahead,
and made me a Wonderbolt

00:43.490 --> 00:45.290
on the first day.

00:46.150 --> 00:47.660
Got a letter here
for Rainbow Dash.

00:52.060 --> 00:53.790
I... didn't get in.

00:56.430 --> 00:57.860
Gotcha!

00:59.820 --> 01:03.490
You guys are so gullible.
Like I wasn't gonna get in!

01:04.240 --> 01:08.500
I'm just sooooooooo
happy for you!

01:09.000 --> 01:11.140
Uh... thanks?

01:13.500 --> 01:16.310
Pinkie Pie?
I kinda need to get going.

01:19.000 --> 01:20.450
Okay. I'm done!

01:21.520 --> 01:24.980
Sooner I get there,
sooner I get to show off my stuff!

01:25.950 --> 01:27.360
See you guys in a week!

01:27.510 --> 01:28.420
Good luck!

01:28.570 --> 01:30.690
Won't need it!

01:32.360 --> 01:36.280
DON'T FORGET TO WRITE!

01:40.240 --> 01:42.600
Do you think she heard me?

01:44.940 --> 01:49.940
